
1  

Kijuka EJAKAIT Natan mama ejai Daudi. Kobu ŋesi mama ejai, kotema ŋes atiar, “Ajaas ituŋa iarei toma ore ediopet; abarit ediopet, kicana loce. 
2  Ajaas ekabaran isipanin luipu noi luka aituk ka amerekekin: 
3  Konye amamei lokican ibore, dimarai amerekek adiopet nakalol, naagweli ŋesi, kitan da: kopoloor nepepe kaŋes ka ikedwe; komorete kaŋes ikenyamat luikidioko, komasete kaikopoke, koperi katorobuke, kosubite bala erai akokuke. 
4  Kobu ekaloton mama ejai ekabaran, mam abu koyaŋa yenikosipaninike luka aituk ka luka amerekekin apuikin ekaloton loabu kobu mamake, konye koyaŋa imerekek yenika lokican, kopuik etuŋanan loabu kobu mamakeŋ.” 
5  Kinep noi anyunyura naka Daudi aluikin etuŋanan; kotema ŋesi Natan atiar, “Kwape ejaria EJAKAIT, etuŋanan loeswamai ŋun ibusakinit atwanare. 
6  

Egeli imerekek irwan aoŋon, naarai abu kiswama akirot ŋin, ido naarai mam abu kitim.”


7  

Kotema Natan Daudi atiar, “Ijo ŋes etuŋanan ŋol. Inera EJAKAIT, Edeke loka Isirael, kwanata ebe, ‘Abu eoŋ kenyonyoik jo akinyet araun ekabaka loka Isirael, abu kayu jo kakan naka Saul: 
8  Abu kainak jo etogo loka ejakaitikon, aŋor da nuka ejakaitikon katorobukon, kainak jo ekek loka Isirael ka loka Yuda; arai kiikadito ŋul, tikeyatakinit jo ice bobo. 
9  

Kanukinyo imwania akirot naka EJAKAIT, aswam nueroko kakonyeneke? Inom ijo Uria Ekitit kekileŋ, iyana aberuke araun akoniberu, iara ŋes kekileŋ loka idwe luka Amon. 
10  

Aso do mam enyouni ekileŋ kokekikon; naarai imwan ijo eoŋ, iyana aberu naka Uria Ekitit araun akoniberu.’ 
11  

Inera EJAKAIT kwanata ebe, ‘Koany, etonyoikini jo aronis kotogokon, ayaŋaari aŋorokon kakonyenekon, ainakini kes mama ejai eidunyetekon, eperete ŋes kanorokon paaran kaitebeikin. 
12  Naarai iswama ijo kaiyeiyea: konye eswamai eoŋ akirot nln kakonyen nuka Isirael kere paaran kaitebeikin.’ ” 
13  

Kotema Daudi Natan atiar, “Adiaka kama ejai EJAKAIT.” Kotema Natan Daudi atiar, “Alema da EJAKAIT adiakaretekon; mam jo itwani. 
14  

Konye naarai iinak lukasurupo luka EJAKAIT amoromor kanuka aswamisioit ŋin, abeit etwani ikoku yenikiwurikinitai jo.” 
15  

Kolot Natan togoke.

Kinom EJAKAIT ikoku yenaurikini aberu naka Uria Daudi, kodekakin noi. 
16  

Kanuka ŋun kiŋaiŋa Daudi Edeke kanuka ikoku: kikany Daudi eteŋei, koloma, koper kalup, akuare kia. 
17  Konyout imakio lukotogoke, kobwaata kosiepike, aitonyoun ŋes kokwap: konye koŋer, mam da abu konyam atap kakes. 
18  Kosodi kanen, kapaaran nakikanyetekaarei kotwana ikoku. Kokuriakata ikejaanakinak luka Daudi alimokin ŋes ebe atwana ikoku; naarai kobalas ebe, “Koany, naariŋar ikoku ejari, kinera oni kaŋes, mam abu kopup iporotoiwok: ikwaikini lolo ai ŋesi erieba, arai kilimokini ŋes ebe atwana ikoku?” 
19  Konye keanyu Daudi ebe iyeiyeanakinos ikejaanakinakake, kojenik Daudi ebe atwana ikoku: kotema Daudi ikekejaanakinak atiar, “Atwana ikoku?” Kotemasi kesi atiar, “Atwana ŋesi.” 
20  

Kosodi Daudi anyoun kokwap, kiloŋ, kinyonyoik akinyet, kijul anapitoke; koloma togo loka EJAKAIT, koma: kosodi aboŋor togoke: kekotokin atap kibwaikis akonyeneke, konyam. 
21  Kosodete ikekejaanakinak atemar ŋes atiar, “Anyoika nu nuiswama? Naariŋar ikoku ejari ikany ijo eteŋei komony kanuka ikoku; konye naatwania ikoku, inyou, inyam atap.” 
22  

Kotema atiar, “Naariŋar ikoku ejari, abu kekany eteŋei, kamony: naarai abala ebe, ‘Iŋai bo ejeni motoko esiana EJAKAIT mamaka, tetere ejari ikoku?’ 
23  

Konye do atwana, kanukinyo ekanyia bobo eteŋei? Apedori ainyakun ŋes bobo? Alosi eoŋ rwaru mamake, konye mam ŋes eboŋuni mamakaŋ.”


24  

Kipud Daudi Bat-seba akeberu, koloma mamake, koperoto kaŋes: kouru ikoku yenisapat, komaik ekekiror Solomon. Komina EJAKAIT ŋes; 
25  Kijuka akirot konabi Natan, komaik ekekiror Yedidia,

kanuka EJAKAIT.


26  

Kitiji Yoab Raba loka idwe luka Amon, koyaŋa ere loka ekabakane. 
27  Kijuka Yoab ikiyakia mama ejai Daudi kotema atiar, “Etiji Raba, eebo, ayaŋa eoŋ ere loka akipi. 
28  Aso do kotukok ituŋa ice luesalito, kidukur asurokin ere, koyaŋa ŋes: kenyek eoŋ ayaŋaar ere, komaikinai ekakiror.” 
29  Kotukonok Daudi ituŋa kere, kolot Raba kitiji, kirum. 
30  

Kolem ŋesi aboko naka ekabakakec kakouke; alaŋiruke atalat naka esabu, kejaas amor nuka akais nuipu tomake: kitanapikinai akou naka Daudi. Kitolom luŋatuna luka ere luipu noi. 
31  Kitolom da ituŋa lukejaas nen, kibwaik kes kwap kimusemenin, kwap kasua nuboket, kwap kaepei nuka asua, kitotor kes neecweere amatapalin: kiswamak ireria kere luka idwe luka Amon kwaŋin, Koboŋo Daudi ka ituŋa kere Yerusalem.

